类 GJDepthFirst<R,A>

  • java.lang.Object

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    GJVisitor<R,A>

    public class GJDepthFirst<R,A>
extends java.lang.Object
implements GJVisitor<R,A>
    Provides default methods which visit each node in the tree in depth-first order. Your visitors may extend this class.
